            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Returns the smallest rectangle that completely encloses both "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "aRect"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "bRect"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If one of the rectangles has 0 (or negative) width or height, a copy of the other rectangle is returned; but if both have 0 (or negative) width or height, the returned rectangle has its origin at (0.0, 0.0) and has 0 width and height."
